                        </div>
                        <div class="three-column2__txt">
                            <div class="three-column2__ttl">
                                <h3>
                                    <span class="ttl-jp"><small>代表取締役社長</small><br>林 正基</span>
                                    <span class="ttl-eng">Masaki Hayashi</span>
                                </h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="three-column2__body">
